Bestway Rent-a-Car Customer Follow-up SMS Program
www.bestwayrentacar.com

Program Description:
Bestway Rent-a-Car operates a customer follow-up SMS program. After your rental, you may receive 1–2 text messages from us asking about your experience.

Message Frequency:
Approximately 1–2 messages per rental.

Message and Data Rates:
Message and data rates may apply depending on your mobile carrier and plan.

Opt-Out:
Reply STOP at any time to unsubscribe. You will receive no further messages.

Help:
Reply HELP for assistance, or contact us at info@bestwayrentacar.com.

Opt-In Method:
Customers provide their phone number at the time of rental and are informed they may receive a follow-up SMS regarding their experience.

We do not share your information with third parties for marketing purposes.
